title: Whale.War.S05E08.720P--KILLERS edited  No commercials
description:
This is Whale Wars S05 Ep08 Target Acquired in 720P HD


I took KILLERS 720P HD file and edited out the commercials and such. The resulting file is bigger than the original, but I prefer quality over file size, especialy considering this is a re-encode.

The audio is still just a tad off sync throughout the video, but it is a consistent. It is very tolerable. If it still bugs you, use VLC player to offset the audio just a tad.

This was edited and re-encoded using Cyberlink Power Directer 10.
